*ffi-1.1.3 (01 Aug 2012)

  01 Aug 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +ffi-1.1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump. Fix build without UTF8 environment, bug 429304.

*ffi-1.1.0 (24 Jul 2012)

  24 Jul 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +ffi-1.1.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  08 Jul 2012; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> ffi-1.0.11.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #417573).

  17 Jun 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -ffi-1.0.9-r1.ebuild,
  -ffi-1.0.10.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

  06 May 2012; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org> ffi-1.0.9.ebuild:
  ppc64 stable wrt #369573

  03 Jan 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> ffi-1.0.11.ebuild:
  Add rdoc as a general build dependency because it is always included in the
  Rakefile. Fixes bug 397439.

*ffi-1.0.11 (18 Dec 2011)

  18 Dec 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +ffi-1.0.11.ebuild:
  Version bump. Add missing test dependency and fix test task.

  17 Dec 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> ffi-1.0.9.ebuild,
  ffi-1.0.9-r1.ebuild, ffi-1.0.10.ebuild:
  Add ~ia64

*ffi-1.0.10 (24 Oct 2011)

  24 Oct 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +ffi-1.0.10.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  02 Oct 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> ffi-1.0.9.ebuild:
  sparc stable

  28 Sep 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> ffi-1.0.9.ebuild,
  ffi-1.0.9-r1.ebuild:
  Use virtual/libffi instead of dev-libs/libffi in case we have to switch to
  using copy from GCC in future.

